mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
">4. O-uria Mukristu airitanaga kwambiiria Kirundu Umutheru amutongeerie no u maciara ja Kirundu Umutheru&nbsp;<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; joonekanaga utuurone bwawe.</span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:-9.0pt;tab-stops:7.5in" align="left">Indi, Mukristu atiujuri (gutongerwa) ni Kirundu Umutheru niwe&#133;</p>
    <p align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face><font size="7"><span style=" 10.0pt;       ; "><b style=";  10.0pt;       ">3</b></span></font><b style="; font-size: 12.0pt;  10.0pt; font-family: Times New Roman;       ">&nbsp; </b><font size="5"><b>MUKRISTU WA MITUGO YA KIMWIRI</b></font></font>
    </p>
    <p align="left">Mukristu wa mitugo ya kimwiri athuganagia uria oomba kwigwiria ari wengwa nkuruki ya kugwiria Murungu. Endaga gwitongeeria wengwa, o-ta uria mwana umunini eendaga mantu jawe aki, ta antu ba withire bwa nthiguru.</font></span>
    </p>
    <p align="left">Bibilia irluga uju iguru ria Mukristo aria aigwiragia wengwa.</font></span></b>
    </p>
    <p class="MsoBodyText3"><font color="#3030C0" face>&quot;Atana-ba-Aba ntoombire kwaria nabwi ta buri na mukarie jwa kirundu, indi ndaaririe nabwi ta antu ba mukarie jwa mwiri, na kairi ta buri nkenke ndene ya Kristu. Ni iria ndabukundagia, ti biakuria bibiumo ndabwejaga niuntu butingiumba, na kinya nandi butibiumba. Niuntu, kinya nandi butwire na nurakie jwa kimwiri, tontu bwa uria buri na ruriitho na mateta bwingwa; anga buti antu ba mikarie jwa nwiri, na bwitaga na miitire ta ya antu ba nthiguru iji?&nbsp;<span style="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b>(1 Akorintho 3:1-3)</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoBodyText3" align="right">nandi tega ...</font></span></b></p>
