">Wenda kua muntu wa muthemba juriku?</span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in;mso-outline-level:1">MUKRISTU WA MITUGO YA KIMWIRI OOMBIKIA ATIA&nbsp;</span></b>&nbsp;KUUJURWA</b><b style="; font-size: 12.0pt;  10.0pt; font-family: Times New Roman;       "> </b>NI KIRUNDU UMUTHERU?</b></span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:4.5pt;mso-outline-level:1" align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face size="4"><b>TUUJURAGWA (GUTONGEERUA) NI KIRUNDU UMUTHERU NA NJIRA YA WITIKIO</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:4.5pt;mso-outline-level:1" align="left">Tuejaga Akristu na njira ya witikio ndene ya Kristu Mwonokia wetu. Tuujuragwa ni Kirundu Umutheru na njira ya witikio tukiirigagiira Murungu na kuthikiira ruteto rwawe. Womba kuthingata matagario jaja jojathatu...</font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:4.5pt;mso-outline-level:1" align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face><b>1. Menyithia Murungu Ati Nukwenda Kuujurwa Ni Kirundu Umutheru</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:4.5pt;mso-outline-level:1" align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face>&quot;kitharimo-ri, ni kiri baria bari na mpara na nyonta niuntu bwa mantu jaria jaagirite, ni kwithirwa bakanyirua&quot;, <b>(Mathayo 5:6)</b></span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:4.5pt;mso-outline-level:1" align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face><b>2. Umbura Meeyia Jaku</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in;mso-outline-level:1"><font color="#3030C0" face size="3"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman">&quot;Indi tukeethirwa itumburaga meeyia jetu, we ni mwitikua, na kairi naagirite, nawe agaturekera meeyia jetu na atuthambie uthuku bunthe. &quot; <b>(1 Johana 1:9)</b></span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:4.5pt;mso-outline-level:1" align="left"><b>Kuumbura meeyia jetu ni kugita atia?</font></span></b></p>
    <blockquote>
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in">Kuumbura Meeyia&nbsp;<br>
    a.. Witikanagiiria na Murungu ati nuthithitie meeyia.<br>
      <font size="3"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman">b. Ucookagiria Murungu nkatho niuntu bwa gukurekera na gukuthambia na tharike ya&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-size: 12.0pt;  10.0pt; font-family: Times New Roman;  mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman;      ">Jesu Kristu. </span>
    <span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
"><br>
    </span>
    <span style="font-size:12.0pt;10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
">c. Ugarukagira Murungu na ugatigana na meeyia ta kwirira.</span></p>
    </blockquote>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><font color="#3030C0" face><b>3&nbsp;
    Irite Niuntu Bwa Murunqu</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><font color="#3030C0" face>&quot;Kana bukaethia marungo jenu mathaga ja wiyia, ta jari mathaga ja umaramari; indi ciethagieni nthuumba cia Murungu bwingwa, ta buriukite kuuma gikuune, O na marungo jenu jaethagieni mathaga ja Murungu ta jari mathaga ja wagiru.&#148; <b> (Aroma 6:13)</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in">Gutuura utuuro buujuri (gutongeerua) ni Kirundu Umutheru, no rnwanka Jesu atongagiiria mathithio jetu jonthe.</font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><font face="size=&quot;3&quot;"><span style=" mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman;      ">No Mwanka atongeerie uria tugatumira mbeeca cietu, igiita rietu, na magiita jetu ja kunogoka, ngugi cietu, ngwataniro na ndugu na acoore bangi.</span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="right"><b><font size="3" face><span style="      ">Ukumenya matagario jaja jathatu? Twicookere kairi?</span></font></b></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face><b>WIRIGIIRE MURUNGU AKUUJURIE KIRUNDU WAWE UMUTHERU</b></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left">Murungu agakuujuria (gugutongeeria na gukuumbithia) na Kirundu wawe Umutheru wamwirigiiria akuthithirie uu.</font></span></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left">Riikana mariitwa jojairi:</font></span></p>
  <blockquote>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><b><font color="#3030C0" face>1. WATHIKIRE WATHO BWAWE KUUJURWA</span></font></b></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><font color="#3030C0">&nbsp;</span>&quot;Bukoorwetikira kwogitua na ncoobi, niuntu manto jau ja mbogita nijo jaretaga mantu ja umaramari, indi ujuragweni na Kirundu. <b> (Aefeso 5:18)</b></font></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><font color="#3030C0" face>&nbsp;<b>2. IRIGAGIIRA WIRANE BWAWE GUKUJURIA</b></span></font></p>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in"><font color="#3030C0">&nbsp;</span>&quot;Na buu nibu ucamba buria turi nabu mbere yawe, ati kethirwa tukamuromba untu kinya buriku buria bwagirite methone jawe agatuthikiira, na twethirwa nitwiji mma ati nathikagiira maromba jetu jonthe, nou tubwirite kumenya ati turina biria tumurombete. <b>(1Johana 5:14-15)</b></span></font></font></p>
  </blockquote>
    <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="right">kinya nandi&#133;</p>
    <center>

    <div align="center"><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left"><font color="#3030C0" face><b>WOMBA KUUJURWA KIRUNDU UMUTHERU NA NJIRA YA WITIKO</b></font></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left">Njira imwe ya kwonania witikio bwaku ni na maromba.</font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left">WOMBA KUROMBA UJU:</font></span></b></p>
        <div align="center">
        <table border="2" width="90%" bordercolor="#3030C0" bgcolor="#BFBFFF">
        <tr>
        <td width="100%"><font color="#3030C0" face>Mwathani Jesu, ningukwenda utongeeria utuuro bwakwa Mbithagirwa ngitongagiiria utuuro bwakwa ningwa. Nandi ingwitikaniiria nawe ati jaja ni meeyia. Ngutiga meeyia jaja na kwirita kiri we gukwathikira.&nbsp; </span>Ibubwega niuntu bwa kumbujuria O-ta uria uugite.</span></font></td>
        </tr>
        </table>
        </div>
        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left">Wenda kuromba Murungu akujurie na agutongagiirie na akumbithie utuurone bwaku?</font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-right:2.0in" align="left">Wenda kuromba iromba riri nandi?</font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#3030C0"><b>WOMBA KUMENYA ATI NUUJURI (GUTONGEERUA) KIRUNDU&nbsp;UMUTHERU NA NJIRA YA WITIKIO</b></font></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">Nwithuranirite O-ta uria turikitie gukwoneeria ndene ya maratasi jaria jari nyuma?&nbsp;
        Nukwirigiira Murungu na njira ya witikio akuujurie na Kirundu Umutheru?&nbsp;
        </span>Mbica iiji irionania uria umma bwa Bibilia, na witikio na withire bwa nkoro (maoni) bigwatanagira utuurone bwaku bwa Gikristu</span></font></p>
        <blockquote>
          <p class="MsoNormal" align="center">
          <img border="0" src="images/truck1.gif" width="450" height="128"></font></p>
        </blockquote>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p class="MsoNormal">Murunqu augite ati uujurwe ni Kirundu Umutheru. Nariikanirite natwi ati agatucookeria&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
            maromba twamuromba kuringana na wendo bwawe.</span></font></li>
          <li>
            <p class="MsoNormal">Uumba kuujurwa ni Kirundu Umutheru bunka werigiira ati akoojuria wirane bwawe.&nbsp;</span></font></li>
          <li>
            <p class="MsoNormal">Werigira Murunqu akuujuria. agakua inya ya gutuura na uumbe gukujira kiri bangi&nbsp;
            mantu ja Jesu.</span></font></li>
          <li>
            <p class="MsoNormal">Ukoorirua ati wirigagiira Murungu akujuria, na utirigagiira mathuganio jaku.&nbsp; </span>Murungu atirega
            kuujuria wirane bwawe bwa gukuujuria na Kirundu. Murungu ti murongo.</span></font></li>
          <li>
            <p class="MsoNormal">Tontu Murungu ni mwitikua, nandi woomba kumucookeria nkatho niuntu bwa gukuujuria na&nbsp;Kirundu</span> Umutheru, kinya kethirwa utiraona mwanya kinya juriku.</span></font></li>
        </ol>
    </center>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><font color="#2824B8" face>WOMBA GWITA NA MBERE KUUJURWA</span></font></b></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left">Kethira ukeeyia kairi na gutongeeria utuuro bwaku wengwa, no mwanka kuthithia mantu jojairi.<br>
        <br>
        <b><font color="#2824B8">1. </font></b><font color="#2824B8"><b>Umbura meeyia jaku kiri Murungu. (I Johana 1:9)</b></font><font color="#2824B8"><b>&nbsp;</b></font></span><font color="#2824B8">Mucookerie nkatho niuntu bwa urekeri bwawe. Garuka utigane na&nbsp; </span>
        </span>meeyia jaku.&nbsp;</font><br>
        <font color="#2824B8"><b>2. </b></font><font color="#2824B8"><b>Ira Jesu ajukie giti kia wathani bwa utuuro bwaku kairi.&nbsp;</b>Riikana watho bwawe ndene ya <b>Aefeso 5:18</b> na kirikaniro kiawe ndene ya&nbsp;</font><b><font color="#2824B8">( I Johana 5:14-15)</font></b></font></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left">Thingata makinya jaja jojairi magiita jonthe Kirundu Umutheru akuonagia meeyia utuurone bwaku. Uju ukethirwa urina utuuro bwa kugwirua na guciara maciara ja Kirundu.</font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b>IRIGAGIIRA KIRUNDU UMUTHERU EETAGE NA MBERE GUKUUJURIA (KUGUTONGEERIA). UJU NIU JESU KRISTU AKETHIRWA AKARIRITE GITI KIA UNENE BWA UTUURO BWAKU.</font></span></b></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="right"><b>Womba kumenya ati...</font></span></b></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left"><b><font color="#2824B8" face>O-</span>URIA UGEETA NA MBERE KUJUURWA NI KIRUNDU UMUTHERU:</span></font></b></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">1. Matunda ja Kirundu jakoonania utuurone bwaku nkuruki ntuku cionthe. </font><b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(Agalatia 5:22-23)</font></b></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">2. Maromba jaku jakarita ngugi. </font><b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(Jakobo 5:16)</font></b></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">3. Umenyo bwa Bibilia bwaku bukaingia. </font><b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(II Timotheo 3:16-17)</font></b></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">4. Ukagia na inya kuuma kiri Murungu ya gukuujira. </font><b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(Mathithio 1:8)</font></b></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">5. Ukagia na inya kuuma kiri Murungu ya kuumbana na magerio. </font><b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(1Akorintho 10:13)</font></b></span></p>
        6. Ukoomba kuumbana iguru ria irundu bibithuku <b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(1 Johana 4:1-4)</font></b>
        <p align="right"><b>ni untu bwa gitumi&#133;</b></p>
        <div align="center">
        <center>
        <table border="2" width="90%" bordercolor="#2824B8" bgcolor="#BFBFFF">
        <tr>
        <td width="100%">
        <p align="center"><font size="4" color="#2824B8" face><b><span style=" 10.0pt;       ">ITAGA KANISENE</span></b></font></td>
        </tr>
        </table>
        </center>
        </div>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left">Riria nku iri amwe, mwanki ijwakanaga na weeru bubwingi. Ukarita ruku rumwe, na ukarwika guntu kumwe mwanya, karutigaga gwakana.O uu nou kuri na inya gutuura gi Kristo uri wenka.</font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="left">Tirimanaga na Akristu bangi baria baambiritie Jesu Kristu ta Mwonokia na Mwathani wao. Nubwirite gwitaga kanisene naaria antu beetikitie Bibilia ni luku ria umma na naaria Jesu Kristu aathikagirwa. </font><b><font face="color=&quot;#2824B8&quot;">(Ahibrania 10:25)</font></b></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><b><font color="#2824B8" face>KETHIRA IUKU RIRI NIRIGUGUTETHIA, ITU RITHOMERE&nbsp;KANAUE MUNTU UNGI.</span></font></b></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">Uetwe iuku riri ni:</font></span></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><b>Life Ministry Kenya&nbsp;<br>
        P.O. Box 62500&nbsp;<br>
        </span>Nairobi, Kenya</span></b></font></p>
        <p class="MsoNormal" align="right"><b>Mwandiki ni Dr. William R. Bright</font></span></b></p>
    <center>

<hr SIZE="4" WIDTH="90%">
        </center>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
</div>
